<section id="logs" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logs-header">
      <h2>Recent Updates</h2>
      <p>Latest stories and updates from the SV Holdfast journey</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="logs-grid">
      <article class="log-card">
        <div class="log-meta">
          <span class="log-date">March 15</span>
          <span class="log-category">Pacific Crossing</span>
        </div>
        <h3>Halfway across the Pacific - what we've learned</h3>
        <p>After 20 days at sea, we're reflecting on the challenges and incredible moments of this Pacific crossing. The community has been amazing with support and questions.</p>
        <a href="#" class="log-link">
          Read more
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M7 17L17 7M17 7H7M17 7V17"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </article>
      
      <article class="log-card">
        <div class="log-meta">
          <span class="log-date">March 10</span>
          <span class="log-category">Life Aboard</span>
        </div>
        <h3>Living in 200 square feet - space optimization tips</h3>
        <p>After years aboard SV Holdfast, we've learned how to make the most of limited space. Here are our best tips for small-space living that work on land too.</p>
        <a href="#" class="log-link">
          Read more
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M7 17L17 7M17 7H7M17 7V17"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </article>
      
      <article class="log-card">
        <div class="log-meta">
          <span class="log-date">March 5</span>
          <span class="log-category">Adventure</span>
        </div>
        <h3>Storm sailing: When nature shows who's boss</h3>
        <p>Last week's storm was a reminder of how small we are out here. The community's messages of support meant everything during those challenging 48 hours.</p>
        <a href="#" class="log-link">
          Read more
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M7 17L17 7M17 7H7M17 7V17"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .logs-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
  }

  .logs-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .log-card {
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .log-card:hover {
    border-color: #e0e0e0;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .log-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .log-date {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #666666;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .log-category {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    background: #f8f8f8;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .log-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .log-card p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #666666;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .log-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .log-link:hover {
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .logs-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .log-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>